{"tid":2237993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水圍黃店稱遭食環署針對 被逼取消堂食 街坊「感謝日」排隊買外賣示支持","createTime":"2020-10-10T17:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T18:45:35.000Z","uid":173326,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd121a6a6f45da69821ed3817ae8d7cd9e27790c","tid":2237993,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078061&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=26a21b80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078061&h=ea00f585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078061</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>（獨媒報導）天水圍新北江商場內的食店「櫻花樹下」早前於Facebook稱，因遭食環署打壓而需取消堂食，只能提供外賣服務。今日適逢「10.10 全民感謝日」，有人呼籲市民到各黃店消費，櫻花樹下亦推出外賣自取八折優惠。記者中午到店外視察，只見人頭湧湧，高峰期間有20 餘人排隊等候外賣。有街坊表示絕不介意輪候時間變長，日後會繼續幫襯：「呢間店係幫緊手足。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店因為立場而受政府迫害，香港人對黃店嘅支持好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3e7f6fca29d7d8b5fc34431e7d474e44719050","tid":2237993,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"良知係可以當飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d8f69535adc93991e49e9ea08cbb073ea56b2b","tid":2237993,"uid":85339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"係天瑞開既時候好好食<br />\n一搬左去新北江之後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abbd694055e226ba4f775ec4f5ac561d03f68a1","tid":2237993,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8d8f69535adc93991e49e9ea08cbb073ea56b2b","tid":2237993,"uid":85339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T17